reviewText: Edenquest: Pamela Anderson is one hour long, five minutes are a preview of Naked Souls; a movie that Pamela Anderson is in. The movie, if you want to call it that, start off with beautiful topless models. Then we get a little history of Bora Bora, where the movie is being filmed. Along with Pamela Anderson are eight models. They are: Raquel Gardner, Leeann Tweeden, Robyn Killian, Alexander Kabi, Shauna O'Brien, Kim Bachoffer, Michelle Cain Carmin, and Rosie Tenison. During the entire film the ladies are shown toples and in a sixty second scene two of the women are totally nude, but from the waist down in hidden in the water. In that sixty second scene we only see Pamela Anderson nude for a quick second are two. Only about twenty minutes of the film is dedicated to showing topless ladies. The other thirty-five minutes is dedicated to the models activities, photo shoots and scenes of the island. As far as I am concern, nude means no close on. Therefore Edenquest: Pamela Anderson only gets a C- from me.

I read the other reviews, and it appears everybody bought this video for the same reason.  Leeann Tweeden is absolutely beautiful in the video.  If you are a Leean Tweeden fan, you must have this video.  Nuff said.

I was fortunate enough to meet Miss Tweeden in Las Vegas when she used to commentate for the Supercross Series.  She was incredibly sweet and polite, and drop dead gorgeous, of course.  The only item I had for her to sign was the tank top I was wearing.  Needless to say, the tank top has been retired.

LeeAnn Tweeden from ESPN'S Fitness Beach & FX's Toughman... TOPLESS!!  Venus Swimwear model & E! Wild On guest host Raquel Gardner... TOPLESS!! Pamela Anderson... TOPLESS!! Plus alot more hot models! Great video!
